{"tid":1459014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求人不如求己論","createTime":"2019-08-12T15:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:10:23.000Z","uid":156407,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"66383e9443be570a89f2e828d3c39ecb76796600","tid":1459014,"uid":156407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"我今日見到兄弟們再一次為登報去課金<br />\n<br />\n我不能苟同呢個做法<br />\n<br />\n望住2 mil美金瞬間完成目標，但612基金首日募捐都唔夠2mil 美金<br />\n<br />\n只係想問登報嘅意義同作用性有幾大？<br />\n<br />\n你哋可能想用輿論壓力迫使外國支持香港示威者，或者尋求佢哋嘅幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n但係香港只不過係中美，甚至全球對中國政治鬥爭的一個籌碼<br />\n<br />\n香港人再一次依賴他方，不去考慮提升自身實力，改變想法，如何取下一次勝利<br />\n<br />\n揮舞英美國旗，登報都只係手足圍爐取暖嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n要捐就去撐手足"},{"pid":"796569527869a5af50cc35b6c1240c8a65eeda6d","tid":1459014,"uid":156407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:47:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d719a22fc79cb82bc0d7faf9b19025775fd1885b","tid":1459014,"uid":156407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:47:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bca2a13cffc2d375d0f9db76f7fa23dd246a6af","tid":1459014,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:47:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0af8630460c99c72a73221fc6de1a7afdbeca74","tid":1459014,"uid":156407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:47:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f69428a8ff97624e1495eec9b5b7224362551bc7","tid":1459014,"uid":87511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:47:47.000Z","msg":"兩樣都可以做，冇抵觸"},{"pid":"4683e84b9c62d9f9c577a356148f467b64a3768f","tid":1459014,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:49:29.000Z","msg":"佢地個團隊唔知登報架wor。d錢會用得其所架喇"},{"pid":"71737aa313a92a1070e16f6de308c496c4aaf025","tid":1459014,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:49:37.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-a